schools.name: Boerne - Samuel V Champion High School

data.description: Step into a bright and modern home located in the Cielo Ranch/Bluffs of Lost Creek subdivision of Boerne, Texas, just northwest of San Antonio off I-10. This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house boasts a large kitchen with a grand island and bar seating, perfect for entertaining. The living room and kitchen combo features wood beams on the ceiling, adding a touch of elegance. Right off the living room, you'll find a flex room that's ideal for an office or play area. The primary bedroom offers a lavish en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub and large shower. Outside, the covered backyard patio and ample grassy area await your personal touch to create an outdoor paradise. This home combines modern living with the tranquility of the Texas Hill Country.
